“No.”

“Going?”

“I think so.”

“What hotel you going to stop at?”

“I don't know. Is there more than one?”

“Three. You stop at the Schreiber--you'll find it full of Americans.
What ship did you say you came over in?”

“CITY OF ANTWERP.”

